# COMMITTED offline-rebuild caches. notebooks/data/ is ignored above, but two
# subtrees are force-added (git keeps tracking them once added, like
# notebooks/data/results/*.csv): they let the paper rebuild from scratch without
# re-pulling slow seismic data or the flaky Planetary Computer API.
#   notebooks/data/results/      seismic band-power timeseries (CSV)
#   notebooks/data/braid_cache/  derived Sentinel mndwi/channel rasters (npz) +
#                                station pixels (json) + December series (csv);
#                                opera_corridor.npz (cached OPERA flood-water raster)
#   notebooks/data/usgs_iv_*.csv USGS-NWIS discharge+STAGE per gage (small; stage is
#                                not in results/, so needed offline for fig15/fig25)
# To (re)track after adding a new file: git add -f notebooks/data/braid_cache/
